import{polarToCartesian}from'../PolarUtils';/**
 * Only applicable for radial layouts
 * @param {Object} activeCoordinate ChartCoordinate
 * @returns {Object} RadialCursorPoints
 */export function getRadialCursorPoints(activeCoordinate){var{cx,cy,radius,startAngle,endAngle}=activeCoordinate;var startPoint=polarToCartesian(cx,cy,radius,startAngle);var endPoint=polarToCartesian(cx,cy,radius,endAngle);return{points:[startPoint,endPoint],cx,cy,radius,startAngle,endAngle};}
